-- HSBC Hires Chin From ING as Senior Interest-Rates Strategist in London
-- Matthew Brown
-- 2010-08-02T09:28:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/hsbc-hires-chin-from-ing-as-senior-interest-rates-strategist-in-london.html

          
          
             HSBC Holdings Plc , Europe’s biggest
bank by market value, hired  Wilson Chin  as a senior interest-
rates strategist in London, according to two people with
knowledge of the appointment.  
 Chin was previously at ING Groep NV in Amsterdam. He starts
at HSBC this week, said the people, who declined to be
identified because the hiring hasn’t been announced. He will
report to  Steven Major , global head of fixed-income research.  
